artifacts/phase-f10/runtime-backups/

# --- artifacts temporarios/gerados (nao versionar) ---
artifacts/generated/*
!artifacts/generated/.gitkeep
!artifacts/generated/README.md
artifacts/phase-f10/runtime-convergence-report-*.json
artifacts/phase-f10/runtime-inventory-*.json
artifacts/phase-f10/runtime-merge-plan-*.json
